{"type": "article", "id": 13118, "title": "如果你非要在凉鞋里再穿双袜子，这里有几种穿法", "description": "不管好不好看，总有那么多人在尝试。", "date": "2015-08-06T18:42:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2532, "name": "袜子"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 84, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702103349J4X5N6EFmVfKe8UI.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;\">现在无论是</span><a href=\"http://www.pclady.com.cn/tlist/37936.html\" target=\"_blank\">街头风</a><span style=\"text-align:left;\">或者是 T 台上都能看到这种袜子与凉鞋的搭配。</span><span style=\"text-align:left;\">T 台一走秀，模仿的人就多了。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这种将棉袜和凉鞋混搭的穿法，源起于街头的多层次搭配。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t棉袜可选择更多的颜色和花纹，甚至是运动风格的棉袜也可以和凉鞋搭配，越亮丽反差越大的在搭配时更能营造出出位的效果。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t不管好不好看，如果非要在凉鞋里穿双袜子，<a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/fashion/gallery/2015/aug/04/the-good-socks-guide-pairing-socks-with-sandals#img-6\" target=\"_blank\">这里倒是有几种穿法。</a>另外附带一句，关键还是得看腿。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103346GdvTChXUAYz5wj1S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103346QUxTow29dK8n3ZiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103347kU7W8Da46T9Op1tY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103347Aix6fjspM5mUDaCd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103347iNSqoYfW1H4s7UCZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103348jv6GBobkJW75xRM1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103348edhS2a0KmLYcINvX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n"}